Detailed Description

Message representing a route request from Navigator to Server.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum RouteReq::routeType
 

Enumeration values:
slim  Preferred by the GPS-less mode.

Sends enough information that an itinerary can be generated by the client.

full  Preferred by the GPS mode.

Plenty of coordinates ensures good route following, distance and time to goal calculation, and off track detection.
